net.munki.irc.handlers.command

Class IRCCommandAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.munki.irc.handlers.command.IRCCommandAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRCCommandListener, IRCListener, IRCCommandInterface, MessageHandlerInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IRCCommandHandler

    public abstract class IRCCommandAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRCCommandInterface, IRCCommandListener
    Convenience adapter implementing the methods of IRCCommandInterface and IRCCommandListener.
